body.h1: PKPD model for clearance of substance.
body.p: This model is a physiologically based pharmacokinetic model (PKPD) encoded in SBML format for the clearance of substances by the human liver.
body.div: The content of this model has been carefully created in a manual research effort.
This file has been created by Matthias Koenig.
